libs.content:
find_library(sdl2_core_library
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
)

find_library(sdl2main_library
      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths
      /sw
      /opt/local
      /opt/csw
      /opt
    )

find_library(enet_library names enet enet64
        doc "the enet library")
